Source: LEON

Details:
* serves 4

## Ingredients

* 3 small skinless chicken breasts
* 2 tsp dried oregano
* (pinch of chilli powder if you feel courageous)
* 1 tsp ground cumin
* 1 onion peeled and thinly sliced
* 2 red peppers thinly sliced
* 3 tblsp olive oil
* tortillas

## Preparation

* chicken + oregano + chilli + cumin + onion + pepper in a bowl with 2 tblsp olive oil and mix well
* season with sal and pepper, set aside as long as you can
* in a pan heat olive oil over medium heat, cook 7-10min the chicken
* chicken should brown up nicely

